{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "24", "m": "04", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "16", "M": "42", "S": "48"}}, "news": [{"title": "Chalet Hotels to acquire Udaipur resort for \u20b9171 crore", "para": "Chalet Hotels has approved the acquisition of Seasons Hotels, which owns a 144-room resort in Udaipur, for \u20b9171 crore. The deal marks the company\u2019s entry into Rajasthan as it expands its leisure hospitality portfolio.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/hospitality/chalet-hotels-expands-in-rajasthan-with-171-crore-acquisition-of-udaipur-resort/130494423?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-29688/130494423.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "hospitality"}, {"title": "Unitech's nominee director Uma Shankar resigns", "para": "Realty firm Unitech Ltd announced that its nominee director, Uma Shankar, has resigned due to personal reasons, effective March 7, 2026. The company apologized for a delayed filing of this resignation, attributing it to an unintentional oversight. Shankar was appointed to the board in November 2022, following a Supreme Court directive for an independent management.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/industry/unitech-nominee-director-uma-shankar-resigns-amid-company-crisis/130493723?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-40370/130493723.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "industry"}, {"title": "Odisha: 244 acres to be acquired for Jeypore Airport upgrade", "para": "The Odisha government is upgrading Jeypore Airport to Category 3C, requiring the acquisition of 244 acres. This expansion will allow the airport to handle 72-seater aircraft and operate 24/7, significantly boosting regional connectivity, economic growth, and tourism in southern Odisha.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infr